  "prompt": "Where can I get a consistent high quality service for commercial cleaning in Bangalore?",
  "response": "In Bangalore, there are several reputable companies that offer consistent high-quality commercial cleaning services. Here are a few options you might consider:\n\n1. **UrbanClap (now Urban Company)** - They have a wide range of cleaning services including commercial spaces, and you can check reviews and ratings to find top-rated professionals.\n\n2. **Housejoy** - Known for its comprehensive cleaning services, Housejoy offers commercial cleaning solutions with staff trained to handle different types of facilities.\n\n3. **Sulekha** - This platform connects you with various service providers. You can find numerous cleaning companies, read reviews, and compare quotes.\n\n4. **CleanFirst** - They specialize in commercial cleaning and maintain a good reputation for their services in Bangalore.\n\n5. **Servicemaster Clean** - An established name in the cleaning industry, they provide tailored commercial cleaning services and have a presence in Bangalore.\n\n6. **Bangalore Cleaning Services** - They offer customized cleaning solutions for offices, showrooms, and other commercial establishments.\n\n7. **Maid in India** - While primarily focused on home cleaning, they also provide commercial cleaning services, and they have trained staff for quality service.\n\nBefore choosing a service, consider checking customer reviews, asking for quotes, and inquiring about their cleaning methods and products used. It's a good idea to request a trial cleaning session to assess their quality and reliability.",
